semantics.ranking

Class RelationalSystemZ

  • Object
    • RelationalSystemZ

  • public class RelationalSystemZ
extends Object
    Implementation of a system z-like approach to create a ranking function for a first-order conditional knowledge base. Necessary input for such a ranking function is a TolerancePair. Please note that this class does not check any of the restrictions to the first-order language that apply for this approach, but expects all inputs to be correct. This can be ensured using RelationalKnowledgeBaseReader.
    Author:
    Tobias Falke
